rows.label: qst650108_0010
rows.name: More of these guys?!

rows.label: qst650108_0020
rows.name: These blighters just don't know when to quit, do they?

rows.label: qst650108_0030
rows.name: Hmm... They do have the numbers though...

rows.label: qst650108_0040
rows.name: T-elos Re:, what...?

rows.label: qst650108_0050
rows.name:
Come.
I'll put you out of your misery.

rows.label: qst650108_0060
rows.name: Worthless maggots, this place will be your grave.

rows.label: qst650108_0070
rows.name: D-damn you!

rows.label: qst650108_0080
rows.name:
Miserable weaklings...
Did you think you'd be a match for me?

rows.label: qst650108_0085
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]!! (adlib getting stomped on)

rows.label: qst650108_0090
rows.name: Whoa!

rows.label: qst650108_0100
rows.name: Ruthless as always, I see...

rows.label: qst650108_0110
rows.name: T-elos Re:, you alright?

rows.label: qst650108_0120
rows.name: Completely.

rows.label: qst650108_0130
rows.name: Thanks for that!

rows.label: qst650108_0140
rows.name:
That would've taken a lot longer
without you, T-elos Re:...

rows.label: qst650108_0150
rows.name: Though I do wish you'd stop showing off.

rows.label: qst650108_0160
rows.name: Your concern is pointless.

rows.label: qst650108_0170
rows.name: Battle is what Blades are born for.

rows.label: qst650108_0180
rows.name: No need to waste your worries on me.

rows.label: qst650108_0190
rows.name:
Even if it sometimes seems like that's
what you Drivers are born for...

rows.label: qst650108_0200
rows.name: No, look...

rows.label: qst650108_0210
rows.name:
So what, showing concern for our friends
is useless, is that what you're saying?

rows.label: qst650108_0220
rows.name:
Keep talking - I'll stomp you.
Just like I did that last maggot...

rows.label: qst650108_0230
rows.name: Freaky...

rows.label: qst650108_0240
rows.name:
Oh, I give up.
You really are something else, T-elos Re:.

rows.label: qst650108_0250
rows.name: Don't think I've ever seen a Blade like you...

rows.label: qst650108_0260
rows.name: At least there is no doubting her prowess.

rows.label: qst650108_0270
rows.name: Her assistance has proven invaluable.

rows.label: qst650108_0280
rows.name: You're right. She's good to have around.

rows.label: qst650108_0290
rows.name: We'll keep counting on you, all right T-elos Re:?

rows.label: qst650108_0300
rows.name: Hmph...

rows.label: qst650108_0310
rows.name: Ahah...ha...

rows.label: qst650108_0320
rows.name: I'm sure she'll warm to us eventually...
